    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dante's 9 是一款融合卡牌构筑的平台跳跃类肉鸽游戏。你将扮演猫但丁，在与敌方的交锋之中实时使用强力卡牌，对卡牌进行定制和升级，从地狱中杀出重围。你能及时到达第 9 层地狱并力挽狂澜吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>实时战斗系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/fd018f417dd70efdd0409bbb4b291ed0.poster.avif?t=1771710640\" width=1170 height=556 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/fd018f417dd70efdd0409bbb4b291ed0.webm?t=1771710640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/fd018f417dd70efdd0409bbb4b291ed0.mp4?t=1771710640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中使用实时获得的卡牌，一路拼杀，穿越 9 层地狱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>经典卡牌构筑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/0db75d762a669c02359d5b5ec0cf431b.poster.avif?t=1771710640\" width=1170 height=556 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/0db75d762a669c02359d5b5ec0cf431b.webm?t=1771710640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/0db75d762a669c02359d5b5ec0cf431b.mp4?t=1771710640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次旅程中构筑独特的强力牌组，消灭地狱中的恐怖存在！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特贴纸定制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/05712702847ea973915ce7e06f0575f0.poster.avif?t=1771710640\" width=1170 height=556 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/05712702847ea973915ce7e06f0575f0.webm?t=1771710640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293350/extras/05712702847ea973915ce7e06f0575f0.mp4?t=1771710640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过添加贴纸来定制牌组，打造无比强大的组合和搭配</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特性</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特贴纸系统，个性定制卡牌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁多种猫咪，丰富游戏体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌种类 50+</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌方类型 30+ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOSS 战紧张刺激</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOSS 卡牌独具一格 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众多游戏道具等你收集</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁丰富牌组，拓展游戏维度</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共 9 张风格独特的地图邀你探索</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有一键喵喵叫萌翻地狱</p>",
